00:00:00,333 --> 00:00:01,999
HorrorLight.

3
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,766
HorrorLight is a 3D horror game in which you play a character locked in a labyrinth.

4
00:00:06,766 --> 00:00:09,066
It is at the first person view.

5
00:00:09,066 --> 00:00:11,032
You can walk for the discretion …

6
00:00:11,033 --> 00:00:13,133
Or you can run for your life,

7
00:00:13,133 --> 00:00:15,233
Until you find the exit …

8
00:00:15,233 --> 00:00:18,333
Or until you die!

9
00:00:18,333 --> 00:00:22,499
There are 3 modes: Escape, Survivor and Infection.

10
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:26,033
The humans are looking for an exit,

11
00:00:26,033 --> 00:00:29,633
Whereas the monsters are looking for the humans.

12
00:00:30,233 --> 00:00:38,433
All modes are playable in multiplayer and it’s highly recommended to play with friends.

13
00:00:38,433 --> 00:00:44,566
You can use as a human or as a monster a lot of bonuses!

14
00:00:44,566 --> 00:00:48,532
Rayon X vision, invisibility, minimap …

15
00:00:48,533 --> 00:00:51,433
And you can place a lot of trap:

16
00:00:51,433 --> 00:00:56,266
Blind mine, fake exit, immobilize mine…

17
00:00:56,266 --> 00:00:59,132
Be the hunter or the hunted!

18
00:00:59,133 --> 00:01:00,833
Choose your side!

19
00:01:00,833 --> 00:01:04,199
Available in October 2017.

